UPDATED VERSION HERE: http://gamebanana.com/css/maps/167815

Story:
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Terrorists have discovered a secret CT base in an old desert junkyard. CTs have been using it to stockpile weapons against the terrorists. 

Terrorists, blow up the arms depots at A or B.

Counter-Terrorists, stop the Terrorists at all costs!

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALLATION:

Place all files into your:

C:\Program files\Steam\SteamApps\<steam account>counter-strike source\cstrike\maps\

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

LEVEL DESCRIPTION: 

Created for the Junkyard Mapping Contest on gamebanana.com.
